  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Supporting Information: National Casemix Office - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_national_casemix_office">National Casemix Office</xref>
 (<xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_national_casemix_office">NCO</xref>) designs and refines classifications that are used by the English NHS to describe healthcare 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_activity">ACTIVITY</xref>. These classifications underpin the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_national_tariff_payment_system">National Tariff Payment System</xref>
 from costing through to payment, and support local commissioning and performance management.        </p>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_national_casemix_office">National Casemix Office</xref>
 enables the NHS to:        </p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <div>
               <b>
support 
                                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_activity">ACTIVITY</xref>
 costing                    </b>
               <p>: to inform the 
                                <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
                        keyref="supporting_definition_national_tariff_payment_system">National Tariff Payment System</xref>
 processes                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <b>
report on 
                                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
                  <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_activity">ACTIVITY</xref>
 information:                    </b>
               <p>
to ensure that providers are paid for the 
                                <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_service">SERVICES</xref>
 they deliver                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <b>provide information:</b>
               <p>to support epidemiological studies and service planning</p>
            </div>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <b>enable providers and commissioners to use HRGs to benchmark and performance manage</b>
               <p>.</p>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
For further information on the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_national_casemix_office">National Casemix Office</xref>, see the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_digital">NHS Digital</xref>
 website at: 
              <xref href="https://digital.nhs.uk/services/national-casemix-office"
               scope="external"
               format="html">National Casemix Office</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
